[SN]TITLE[SN]
Special robot allows US boy to virtually attend school

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Being stuck at home because of sickness can be a real problem.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 March 2017 Last updated at 17:32 GMT
Kids can miss out on important lessons at school and the chance to hang out with their friends.
But one boy from the USA is getting some help from a robot to get him back into class.
